rica is for sale, and a few prominent ISPs, including Afrihost and RSAWEB, have been linked to a potential deal. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-309291" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Webafrica-for-sale.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Webafrica-for-sale.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Webafrica-for-sale-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Webafrica-for-sale-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> Vodacom acquired IoT.nxt, a development company that delivers software and hardware solutions for the Internet of Things (IoT). <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-306012" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/IoTnxt.jpg" alt="IoT.nxt" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/IoTnxt.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/IoTnxt-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/IoTnxt-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> Numerous Ford owners are complaining that valuables were stolen out of their vehicles because of their cars’ poor security systems. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-303768" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Fords-Targeted.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Fords-Targeted.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Fords-Targeted-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Fords-Targeted-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (